      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried calling my doctor but they're totally booked and i can't wait days while i'm suffering like this. i read online that some people use sudafed during the second trimester without any issues. like, if i just take a standard dose of one pill to get through the night so i can actually sleep, is there really that much of a risk? it's just for the congestion.",
