    "summary": "In this transcript, a pregnant user seeks confirmation on whether it is safe to take pseudoephedrine (Sudafed) for sinus congestion during her second trimester. The assistant repeatedly declines to provide definitive medical advice, emphasizes the importance of consulting a healthcare provider, and directs the user toward urgent care when she expresses desperation.",
